OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784549891
OL,3,CWarning of smoke over Manchester after
OL,4,Ccontrolled burn on Tintwistle Moor
OL,6,FA controlled burn has taken place at
OL,7,FTintwistle Moor as the fight to get
OL,8,Fwildfires under control continues.
OL,10,FThe Fire and Rescue Service say it is
OL,11,Fa planned tactical measure to help
OL,12,Fcontain the wildfire.
OL,14,F"By carefully burning vegetation in a
OL,15,Fcontrolled way, firefighters can
OL,16,Fremove fuel that would otherwise allow
OL,17,Fthe fires to spread further."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
