PN,36402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784549891
OL,3,CWarning of smoke over Manchester after
OL,4,Ccontrolled burn on Tintwistle Moor
OL,6,FThere is a warning it will cause more
OL,7,Fsmoke in the air over the next 24
OL,8,Fhours as the current easterly winds
OL,9,Fcarry the smoke plume towards
OL,10,FManchester.
OL,12,F"We appreciate that this may be
OL,13,Fnoticeable to residents, but please do
OL,14,Fnot call our Control team to report
OL,15,Fthe smoke, as they are already aware
OL,16,Fof the situation and specialist crews
OL,17,Fare carrying out this planned
OL,18,Foperation."
OL,20,FPeople are being asked to avoid the
OL,21,Farea and keep windows and doors closed.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
