PN,36403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784549891
OL,3,CWarning of smoke over Manchester after
OL,4,Ccontrolled burn on Tintwistle Moor
OL,6,FTwo helicopters are dropping water on
OL,7,Fboth the Tintwistle Moor wildfire and
OL,8,Fa separate wildfire at Dovestone
OL,9,FReservoir.
OL,11,FDerbyshire Fire & Rescue Service and
OL,12,FGreater Manchester Fire & Rescue
OL,13,FService are continuing to work closely
OL,14,Fto share specialist resources.
OL,16,FGreater Manchester Fire and Rescue
OL,17,Fhave put out another warning about the
OL,18,Fuse of barbeques on the dry moorland,
OL,19,Fsaying:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
