PN,36404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1784549891
OL,3,CWarning of smoke over Manchester after
OL,4,Ccontrolled burn on Tintwistle Moor
OL,6,F"Our firefighters continue to tackle
OL,7,Ftwo major moorland fires at Swineshaw
OL,8,Fand Dovestones and this weekend, we
OL,9,Fhave already seen people visiting the
OL,10,Farea and lighting BBQs."
OL,12,FPolice made two more arrests in
OL,13,Fconnection with the Dovestone moorland
OL,14,Ffire, both have been bailed.
OL,16,FShania Care-Slede, 20 of Market
OL,17,FStreet, Hyde has been charged with
OL,18,Farson. She has been bailed and will
OL,19,Fappear again at Manchester Crown Court
OL,20,Fon August 18.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/4
